        <h2 class="artical-title">How Can I Be Sure of the Quality of My Lab-Grown Diamond?</h2>
        <p>When you decide to purchase a diamond, it’s generally to mark an important milestone in your life. You may have just earned your first salary, or you might even be picking out a diamond ring for your engagement. Whatever the reason, the purchase of a diamond can be an emotional affair. And while it is easy to get caught up in the moment, it’s vital that you ensure that the diamond you get is the diamond you’ve paid for. But, without the requisite knowledge or technical knowhow, how do you know if the diamond you’ve been given is actually the right weight, cut or clarity that you’ve asked for?</p>
